            <title>[HIVE-25707] SchemaTool may leave the metastore in-between upgrade steps</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-25707</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;it seems like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;schematool runs the sql files via beeline&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;autocommit is turned on&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;pressing ctrl+c or killing the process will result in an invalid schema&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/6e02f6164385a370ee8014c795bee1fa423d7937/beeline/src/java/org/apache/hive/beeline/schematool/HiveSchemaTool.java#L79&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/6e02f6164385a370ee8014c795bee1fa423d7937/beeline/src/java/org/apache/hive/beeline/schematool/HiveSchemaTool.java#L79&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
